{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:1","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"ms2\">HISTOIRE DE SALOMON<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"mr\">Ch. 1 \u00e0 9. (Ac 7:47.)<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">Salomon roi. \u2014 Dieu lui accorde sagesse et gloire<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-12: cf. (1 Ch 21:29. 1 R 3:1-15.) (Lu 11:13. Ja 1:5-7. Pr 2:3-9.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Salomon, fils de David, s\u2019affermit dans son r\u00e8gne; l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu, fut avec lui, et l\u2019\u00e9leva \u00e0 un haut degr\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.2","name":"2 Chroniques 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.30","name":"1 Chroniques 29:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Salomon donna des ordres \u00e0 tout Isra\u00ebl, aux chefs de milliers et de centaines, aux juges, aux princes de tout Isra\u00ebl, aux chefs des maisons paternelles;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.3","name":"2 Chroniques 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>et Salomon se rendit avec toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e au haut lieu qui \u00e9tait \u00e0 Gabaon. L\u00e0 se trouvait la tente d\u2019assignation de Dieu, faite dans le d\u00e9sert par Mo\u00efse, serviteur de l\u2019\u00c9ternel;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.4","name":"2 Chroniques 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.2","name":"2 Chroniques 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>mais l\u2019arche de Dieu avait \u00e9t\u00e9 transport\u00e9e par David de Kirjath-Jearim \u00e0 la place qu\u2019il lui avait pr\u00e9par\u00e9e, car il avait dress\u00e9 pour elle une tente \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.5","name":"2 Chroniques 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.3","name":"2 Chroniques 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>L\u00e0 se trouvait aussi, devant le tabernacle de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, l\u2019autel d\u2019airain qu\u2019avait fait Betsaleel, fils d\u2019Uri, fils de Hur. Salomon et l\u2019assembl\u00e9e cherch\u00e8rent l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.6","name":"2 Chroniques 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.4","name":"2 Chroniques 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Et ce fut l\u00e0, sur l\u2019autel d\u2019airain qui \u00e9tait devant la tente d\u2019assignation, que Salomon offrit \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel mille holocaustes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.7","name":"2 Chroniques 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.5","name":"2 Chroniques 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Pendant la nuit, Dieu apparut \u00e0 Salomon et lui dit: Demande ce que tu veux que je te donne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.8","name":"2 Chroniques 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.6","name":"2 Chroniques 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Salomon r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 Dieu: Tu as trait\u00e9 David, mon p\u00e8re, avec une grande bienveillance, et tu m\u2019as fait r\u00e9gner \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.9","name":"2 Chroniques 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.7","name":"2 Chroniques 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Maintenant, \u00c9ternel Dieu, que ta promesse \u00e0 David, mon p\u00e8re, s\u2019accomplisse, puisque tu m\u2019as fait r\u00e9gner sur un peuple nombreux comme la poussi\u00e8re de la terre!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.10","name":"2 Chroniques 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.8","name":"2 Chroniques 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Accorde-moi donc de la sagesse et de l\u2019intelligence, afin que je sache me conduire \u00e0 la t\u00eate de ce peuple! Car qui pourrait juger ton peuple, ce peuple si grand?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.11","name":"2 Chroniques 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.9","name":"2 Chroniques 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Dieu dit \u00e0 Salomon: Puisque c\u2019est l\u00e0 ce qui est dans ton c\u0153ur, puisque tu ne demandes ni des richesses, ni des biens, ni de la gloire, ni la mort de tes ennemis, ni m\u00eame une longue vie, et que tu demandes pour toi de la sagesse et de l\u2019intelligence afin de juger mon peuple sur lequel je t\u2019ai fait r\u00e9gner,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.12","name":"2 Chroniques 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.10","name":"2 Chroniques 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>la sagesse et l\u2019intelligence te sont accord\u00e9es. Je te donnerai, en outre, des richesses, des biens et de la gloire, comme n\u2019en a jamais eu aucun roi avant toi et comme n\u2019en aura aucun apr\u00e8s toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.13","name":"2 Chroniques 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.11","name":"2 Chroniques 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-17: cf. 1 R 3:15-28; 10:26-29.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Salomon revint \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, apr\u00e8s avoir quitt\u00e9 le haut lieu qui \u00e9tait \u00e0 Gabaon et la tente d\u2019assignation. Et il r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.14","name":"2 Chroniques 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.12","name":"2 Chroniques 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Salomon rassembla des chars et de la cavalerie; il avait quatorze cents chars et douze mille cavaliers, qu\u2019il pla\u00e7a dans les villes o\u00f9 il tenait ses chars et \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem pr\u00e8s du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.15","name":"2 Chroniques 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.13","name":"2 Chroniques 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Le roi rendit l\u2019argent et l\u2019or aussi communs \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem que les pierres, et les c\u00e8dres aussi communs que les sycomores qui croissent dans la plaine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.16","name":"2 Chroniques 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.14","name":"2 Chroniques 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>C\u2019\u00e9tait de l\u2019\u00c9gypte que Salomon tirait ses chevaux; une caravane de marchands du roi allait les chercher par troupes \u00e0 un prix fixe;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.17","name":"2 Chroniques 1:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.15","name":"2 Chroniques 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 1:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.1.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>on faisait monter et sortir d\u2019\u00c9gypte un char pour six cents sicles d\u2019argent, et un cheval pour cent cinquante sicles. Ils en amenaient de m\u00eame avec eux pour tous les rois des H\u00e9thiens et pour les rois de Syrie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.1","name":"2 Chroniques 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.16","name":"2 Chroniques 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb58951f6.85628562');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb58951f6.85628562\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb58951f6.85628562","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb58951f6.85628562'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb58951f6.85628562\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}